        <body>
            <div type="page" n="1" facs="#L1916_267_img_1">
                <opener>
                    <address>
                <addrLine>Piaras Béaslaí, 25 Lindsay Rd, <del>L</del> Glasnevin, <hi rend="underline">Dublin</hi></addrLine>
                </address>
                    <dateline>
                        <date when="1916-01-11">11-1-16</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p> Annso dhom arís &amp; uaigneas orm indiaidh B. Átha Cliath. Níor bhuail an
                    taingeal liom. Is dóca go raibh sé imthighte go luath. Ar thugais cuairt ar P. Ó
                    Shoin. Abair le Tadgh Scannell an rud sin a dhéanamh </p>
                <signed>M.</signed>
                <!-- a problem could be that the address line is transcribed at the end of the text -->
            </div>
